  "name": "RPlog_Battle_of_Selene_Part_II",
  "title": "Storming the Palace of Selene",
  "summary": "A CSA/ESPO commando force, abetted by turncoat Imperial troops, lands at the Selene palace to install Lorn Rhys as Emperor by killing the Sith Sabbathius Osbourne. While Lorn, shielded by his bodyguard Morrison and the wolfman Zrak, advances toward the inner sanctum, the bulk of the fighting becomes a brutal corridor war between the ESPO strike team and the palace garrison. The defenders, rallied by the fanatical Colonel Imral, throw E-Web emplacements, barricades, and nerve gas at the attackers, while the turncoat Raika shells the blast doors from outside with a captured tank. The ESPO commander dies covering his men, Imral falls to a final desperate melee, and the strike team's slicer rigs a turbolift bomb that breaches the lower level, clearing the way for the team to descend the shaft and press the assault.",
